Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识为{\fnsimhei\fs20}JCSⅢ{\r}  血压触诊60
